summary:
Welcome to Conjure Sprrigan spell mod.
this mod adds you a conjure sprrigan spell to the game,you can buy it on the collage.
the sprrigan can be invisible,can make animals to fight for him,he has 100% resistance to poison and 30% weakness to fire. Please like,subscribe and leave a comment. ENJOY!
